{
  "stem": "9665.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I arrived in Antwerp, the first thing we did was writing a letter to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had in Switzerland a yeshiva [NON-ENGLISH] by the name of Leizar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We wrote to him, and he forward that letter to Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there was no communication between Holland and Belgium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Belgium occupied France and France Libre, unoccupied.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no communication-- so wherever we arrived, from Brussels again, I wrote to Leizar and Leizar sent the letter through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my name during the war time was Adrian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All during the flight, Adrian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I always signed with Adrian, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Adrian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was written in such a way because the Germans opened the letters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there was a censor, that one could make out what it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my family understood where I was, and that I got out all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Brussels, we stayed four days, three or four days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we went-- we made arrangement to find the [NON-ENGLISH] in Nancy, which was the occupied France.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went into the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are told there will be 12 of us in the train, and we should be dressed down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We shouldn't be dressed up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were dressed down anyhow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll show you later on a photo the way we were dressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were some women out of the 12 which were a little bit dressed up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were wearing a hat with a feather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that worried us a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We arrived in the middle of the night, at 2:00 or 3:00 in the morning in Nancy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went into a waiting room where there would have been 400 or 500 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to wait for the next train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told the train is at such and such a, a place, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
